text: 305 is a number. It comes after 304 and before 306. == In mathematics == * 305 is an odd number. * It is a composite number, which means it has more than two factors. * The prime factorization of 305 is: 305 = 5 Ã— 61 * The digits of 305 add up to 8 (3 + 0 + 5 = 8). == In measurement == * 305 is the number of millimeters in a foot. == In other areas == * Area code 305 is a telephone area code for Miami, Florida, in the United States.
